---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">魔都ACGN活动交流群-资讯站</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Shanghai Anime Docs</p>
      <p class="hero-tagline">这是一个隶属于SHACGN的资讯站</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/guide/exhibit/BilibiliWorldBasicInfo/" class="btn btn-brand">BW2026</a>
        <a href="/guide/concert/BilibiliMacroLinkBasicInfo/" class="btn btn-brand">BML2026</a>
        <a href="/guide/exhibit/ChinaJoyBasicInfo/" class="btn btn-brand">ChinaJoy</a>
        <a href="/guide/others/JP2025/" class="btn btn-brand">2025·闪击日本攻略</a>
        <a href="/guide/others/ShanghaiTravelGuide_Anime/" class="btn btn-brand">上海游物推荐</a>
      </div>
      <span class="btn btn-alt">陆续增加中...</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      <img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/activity-plat/static/20250603/4920177e4bf9eb2b0fd8dacba0e5dbf8/hLC8OJDn7U.jpg" alt="BW2026封面" referrerPolicy="no-referrer">
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="feature-card warn">
      <h2>警告⚠️</h2>
      <p>未经证实的消息不要转发。但是各位还是请注意安全。不接受陌生人食物！</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h2>本站建立的目的性</h2>
      <p>汇聚全网 ACGN 活动资源，打造魔都最全的 ACGN 活动信息平台！</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h2>精准定位，快速查找</h2>
      <p>通过便捷的筛选功能，快速找到你心仪的活动，不再错过任何精彩瞬间！</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h2>实时更新，一手掌握</h2>
      <p>一手资源，实时更新活动信息，让你永远快人一步！</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .hero-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 3.2em;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand2));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.3em;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all .2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-brand {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand2));
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
  }

  .btn-brand:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 105, 180, .3);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .btn-alt {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px dashed var(--border);
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .hero-image {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 420px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .features {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px 60px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--pad);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .feature-card.warn {
    border-left: 4px solid #ff4d4f;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 77, 79, .05), transparent);
  }

  .feature-card h2 {
    font-size: var(--h2);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: var(--base);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-image {
      width: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>
